715.name: Minion Instability
715.flavourtext: Even in death, they have their uses. They just need a little encouragement.

716.name: Conduit
716.flavourtext: To me, brave companions! Feel my radiance flow through you!

717.name: Acrobatics
717.flavourtext: Light and unadorned, like wind on water, you will be.

718.name: Iron Reflexes
718.flavourtext: Why should I dodge blows that I do not fear?

719.name: Resolute Technique
719.flavourtext: Great tacticians learn that consistency often trumps potential.

720.name: Unwavering Stance
720.flavourtext: Stand your ground, child, keep your senses. The pain is fleeting, but victory is forever.

721.name: Chaos Inoculation
721.flavourtext: Give up everything in pursuit of greatness - even life itself.

722.name: Eldritch Battery
722.flavourtext: What need have I for defence when my enemies are reduced to ash and splinters?

723.name: Blood Magic
723.flavourtext: Lay open your veins, and draw power from your own spilled life.

746.name: Necromantic Aegis
746.flavourtext: I give you everything, my pets. My trust, my strength, my safety. Do not disappoint me.

747.name: Pain Attunement
747.flavourtext: Embrace the pain, drink it in. Your enemies will know your agony tenfold.

748.name: Elemental Equilibrium
748.flavourtext: Balance is good in all things, but especially in the realm of magic.

750.name: Iron Grip
750.flavourtext: Legend tells of bows so powerful that only giants could draw them back.

751.name: Point Blank
751.flavourtext: Look your foe in the eyes before you pierce him. Delight in his fear.

752.name: Arrow Dancing
752.flavourtext: Let the whistling of arrows and stones be your music.

753.name: Phase Acrobatics
753.flavourtext: With enough practice, you can feel the spells coming before they're even cast.
